            "body": "<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">Hi,</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">I'll keep this straight.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">Most web developers don't realize this until it blows up , <b>the majority of small business websites are already vulnerable</b>, even when they look \"fine\" on the surface.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">We run automated external security free scans on live websites. When we scan agency-managed sites, we regularly find:</div>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\">\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">Exposed admin endpoints</div>\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\">\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">Outdated plugins/themes with known exploits</div>\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\">\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">Missing or weak firewall rules</div>\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\">\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">Security headers not set (easy attack surface)</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">This is usually how it plays out:<br>\nSite works perfectly \u2192 gets compromised quietly \u2192 emails stop, Google flags it, or traffic drops \u2192 <b>the client points the finger at the developer</b>.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">That's exactly why I'm reaching out.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">We built <b>ShadowScan</b> to help agencies <b>find vulnerabilities before attackers do, and secure sites without adding workload</b>.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">I'm not asking you to take my word for it.<br>\nI'm asking you to <b>see it yourself</b>.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">\ud83d\udc49 Run a free scan on <b>any WordPress site you manage</b>: <a style=\"margin:0px;\" title=\"https://shadowscan.com.au/contact\" class=\"ex-x_OWAAutoLink\" id=\"ex-OWAfd9c8e87-b17e-271d-b009-fb0139b6a59e\" href=\"https://shadowscan.com.au/contact\">Request a Free Security Scan | ShadowScan</a></div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">If it comes back clean, you've got proof and peace of mind.<br>\nIf it doesn't, you'll immediately see why agencies partner with us instead of trying to manage security internally.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><b>How partnerships usually work:</b></div>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\">\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">\u2705 <b>100% white-label available</b> (your brand, your client, we stay invisible)</div>\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\">\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">\u2705 Or referral-based if you prefer</div>\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\">\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">\u2705 We handle security end-to-end , no tickets, no extra staff</div>\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\">\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">\u2705 You look proactive instead of reactive when something goes wrong</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">If the scan flags issues, I'm happy to walk you through what they mean and whether a partnership even makes sense for you.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">The scan is free.<br>\nDealing with a hacked client site never is.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">Regards,<br>\n<b>Bryan</b><br>\nShadowScan<br>\nWebsite Security &amp; Monitoring</div>\n<div style=\"margin:1em 0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">P.S. Attacks don't target \"big businesses\" anymore - they target <b>unprotected websites</b>.</div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px;font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><br></div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><br></div>\n<div class=\"ex-elementToProof\" id=\"ex-Signature\">\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><br></div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><b>Kind Regards</b></div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\">Bryan Bridle - Website Security Consultant </div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><br></div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><br></div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><b>Website</b>:<a title=\"https://shadowscans.lovable.app\" class=\"ex-OWAAutoLink\" id=\"ex-OWA6eb98401-3b82-d7ef-7f4d-a05e2828248c\" href=\"https://shadowscans.lovable.app\"> ShadowScan - WordPress Security Experts</a></div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><b>Email</b>: Bbridle@shadowscan.com.au</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><b>Phone</b>: 0480 465 208</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos, 'Aptos_EmbeddedFont', 'Aptos_MSFontService', Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);\" class=\"ex-elementToProof\"><br></div>\n</div>",
